title: USGS, Chile earthquake shake map at 3 second interval, Feb 27, 2010, Chile
name: USGS, Chile earthquake shake map at 3 second interval, Feb 27, 2010, Chile
description: The poly shapefile is based on data released by USGS. It shows shakemap 3 second after the quake. Look elsewhere on Finder for other shake maps such as vertical movement as well as time intervals shake maps for 0.3 second, 1 seconds and 3 seconds interval.
